	<p>
		My work spans event-driven architectures, microservices, and cloud-native platforms. I'm particularly
		interested in the messy, practical side of distributed architecture: data ownership, consistency
		models, service boundaries, and how organizational structure shapes system design.
	</p>

	<p>
